Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this job start from tomorrow evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.33,0:00:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right. I guess we should be\Non the lookout from around five.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The expected enemy goes by the name,\N"New Breed Front."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Our role is to prevent terrorist attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.37,0:00:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and obtain any info about\Nthe enemy organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:00:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong, Fumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you read our orders carefully?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Our job this time out is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,to get intel on the New Breed Front's\Nheadquarters and source of funding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.49,0:01:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't say anything\Nabout preventing terrorist attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.95,0:01:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't just stand by\Nand do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.12,0:01:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Fumiya, we mustn't get\Nour priorities mixed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to capture the terrorists\Nin order to gather information.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.74,0:01:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And if that prevents a terrorist act\Nas a result, it's all to the good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we prioritize the prevention\Nof terrorist attacks and kill them all,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.58,0:01:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that would mean we failed in our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.29,0:01:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Among the Yotsuba branch families,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the Kuroba Family is in charge\Nof gathering intelligence,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and we are expected to accomplish our\Nmissions rather than worry about justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\shad2\fs39\bord0\fnOpen Sans\b0\3c&H000000&\u1\c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H000000&\pos(434,96)\clip(124,46,316,128)\t(0,140,\clip(124,46,746,154))}APRIL 7, 2096 - TOKYO OFFSHORE TOWER
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming today,\NMiyuki and Tatsuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you for inviting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Erika and the others aren't coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:04:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No. She said it was a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just like Erika.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, the view\Nfrom the top floor here is breathtaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo Offshore Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan's first hyperbuilding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,360 floors aboveground\Nand 36 floors underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the Sky Lounge\Non the top floor is 2,000 meters high...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but this exceeds my expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, being at this height\Nmakes me a tad nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Would the building collapse\Nin an accident or earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This building is supported\Nby four gigantic pillars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Each pillar stands erect\Ndue to the gyroscopic effect of the flywheels
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,which have been installed on the 36th\Nunderground floor and on every 60th floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,starting with the first underground floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The flywheels wouldn't stop\Noperating during a power outage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the magicians who are stationed\Nunderground will make the flywheels spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They also reduce the friction\Nof the vibration control dampers
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that support the pillars and enhance\Nthe effectiveness of the base isolation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unusual for magicians\Nto be involved in safety measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Cases like this are extremely rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Honoka, Shizuku,\Nwe're going to step out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well... Miyuki and Tatsuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you also guests at this party?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Our friend invited us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.83,0:05:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here on behalf\Nof our aunt, Mr. Hayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Madam sent me here\Nto keep an eye on things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Does my aunt have concerns\Nabout this party?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:06:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because this is the first time a building\Nin Japan has magicians involved in this manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam hopes that nothing happens here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, aren't you working\Nat the entrance ceremony tomorrow, Miyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My advice would be\Nto get plenty of rest for the occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll consult with my brother,\Nand we'll leave the party at a suitable time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for being overbearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you've come at a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Say hello to Miyuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Minami Sakurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise, it's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai here is the niece\Nof Honami Sakurai
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,who served as Madam Miya's\Npersonal attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe she could be useful\Nto you, as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,so I would ask you to keep her in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.66,0:07:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If I ever need help with something,\NI'll count on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I am honored by those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't hesitate\Nto ask me to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we had best be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a visual confirmation\Nof two suspicious-looking people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They're dressed\Nin power company work uniforms
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and appear to be heading toward the\Ninspection port of the submarine power cables.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you think they're agents\Ndisguised as utility workers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yami...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I didn't think\Nyou'd be that surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,S-o-r-r-y.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Never mind! Just get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,True, we are working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's why I apologized.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Yami,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,what should we do about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The head of the family ordered us\Nto detain agents of the New Breed Front.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't know if they're members\Nof that organization unless we capture them,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but the issue is,\Nwhen do we capture them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if they try\Nto tamper with the power cables,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,do we catch them\Nbefore or after their work is done?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We should obviously\Ncapture them beforehand, duh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.95,0:09:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yami, watch your language.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it so obvious to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they're plotting\Na terrorist attack, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.87,0:10:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural that we stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my opinion anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If we were police officers, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you think about it\Nin terms of our objective,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't it be easier and more efficient if we\Nwaited for the terrorists to let their guard down
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,after they've completed their task?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If we interfere beforehand,\Nwhen they have their guard up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,there's more of a risk\Nthat they'll counterattack. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're right, Sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't just watch those bastards\Nengage in despicable acts of terrorism!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't sound like a girl there,\Nbut I agree with what you're saying, personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I do like your cheap sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cheap"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,let's get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fnOpen Sans Extrabold\b0\c&HFFFEFC&\3c&H1D3EDF&\pos(702,68)}VISITOR ARC XII
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I'll cloak the cabin\Nwith Perfect Diffusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll send you in\Nwith Mock Teleportation. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. Fly me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Magicians... But it looks like\Nthey haven't noticed Perfect Diffusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister's skills just keep improving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:12:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Direct Pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's less leakage of residual Psions\Nthan on our mission three months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You've improved yet again, Fumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Fumiya is the attacker,\Nand I'm the backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important that the enemy\Ndoesn't notice the backup,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but the attacker's role is to subdue the enemy\Nin a minimal amount of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You've become a dependable boy, Fumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if your appearance isn't there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done here, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.45,0:13:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Are you going in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like there are\Nbackup troops hiding here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't sense any magicians watchin' us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go again!\NWhen you're a girl, you don't drop your g's!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Yoru, Lady Yami, are you safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We've captured two prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You know our location, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we pick you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get close enough to see us,\Nthat's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish, Lady Yoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this Psionic wave?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Fumiya fighting someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayako is there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They've already captured the enemy.\NSkillfully executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy belongs to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"New Breed Front," a group\Nof radical magician supremacists.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, is something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just blown away\Nby the lineup of guests at this party.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, Yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to send over the prisoners first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Two prisoners, confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can come aboard, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "miss," not "sir"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He put aside his pride to cross-dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to ruin that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir... I mean "miss"...\NMy humble apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're ruining it more than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not cross-dressing!\NThis is a disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, it's a brilliant disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even we would never suspect\Nit was you, Master Fumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.37,0:16:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me by my real name!\NThat makes the disguise pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We're wasting time here. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And Yami, don't lose your cool. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shizuku, Honoka, congratulations\Non advancing to the next grade!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.04,0:16:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Sister and Honoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations. Both of you have\Nexcellent grades. That's truly wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Honoka, I hear\Nyou have a crush on someone. Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I can't let that go by!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that, Mr. Kitayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, what were you really thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Fumiya and Ayako were fighting\Nradicalized magicians near this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Mr. Hayama is here to keep an eye on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it has something to do with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know about a group\Ncalled the "New Breed Front"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they a group standing up\Nagainst anti-magic prejudice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They're an extremist group claiming that\Nmagicians are the most evolved form of humans
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and are trying to build a society\Nwhere magicians reign supreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a troublesome group
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that are willing to resort to armed conflict\Nto liberate the oppressed magicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.91,0:17:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What do such extremists\Nwant with this building?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know\Nwhat the New Breed Front's goal is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, Fumiya and Ayako have prevented...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the sabotage of the power cables\Nthat provide electricity to this tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope it ends there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\shad2\fs34\bord0\fnOpen Sans\b0\3c&H000000&\u1\c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H000000&\pos(644,64)\clip(8,12,186,122)\t(0,250,\clip(8,12,1274,116))}APRIL 7, 2096 - TOKYO OFFSHORE TOWER - 35th UNDERGROUND FLOOR - WAITING ROOM FOR MAGICIANS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.74,0:18:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Leader, the power supply hasn't stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems they failed to cut the cable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move on to Plan B.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,After incapacitating the security guards\Nand magicians on this floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll take over the power control room\Non the 34th underground floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll disconnect\Nthe power supply to the flywheels...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and contain the control center\Non the first underground floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, be extremely sparing\Nwith your use of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone on the lowest floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's empty just as our prior info stated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we'll gain total control\Nof the 34th floor as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:19:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The posture stabilization flywheels\Nhave stopped moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, this building will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The walls and pillars aren't damaged.\NIt won't fall right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the New Breed Front.\NOur aim is to restore the rights of magicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't intend to harm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We just want you to witness\Nwhat will happen here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They hijacked the control center\Non the first underground floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There should've been security guards...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but they must've taken them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Magicians are being used as slave labor\Ndeep in the bowels of this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Slave labor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard they were well-treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's work\Nthat doesn't allow them to escape
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,should disaster strike\Non the 35th underground floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if they've been ordered\Nto be buried alive in such a scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As a group seeking to restore\Nthe rights of magicians
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and as members of a civilized society,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't allow these antiquated\Npractices of human sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they were trapped inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,as far as I know, the underground would\Nbecome a shelter where they could survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As a sign of protest, we are going to set off\Na bomb in this building one hour from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone who is in there now,\Nplease evacuate immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if anyone tries to interfere with us,\Nwe will blow up the building right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We do not wish to have\Na large number of casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.66,0:22:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather, we hope you make the wise decision\Nto become witnesses to history.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.29,0:22:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess hoping that nothing would happen\Nwas too much to ask for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.45,0:23:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fnOpen Sans Extrabold\b0\c&HFFFEFC&\3c&H1D3EDF&\pos(702,68)}VISITOR ARC XIII